research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33270:research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3986:research/history/logs/agent_round_0172.stdout.log:11222:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式可写为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `{u_i}` 是由共享低秩 basis 导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧先通过轻量 shared bottleneck / router 得到 shared 分支系数与少量激活 expert，再在对应静态库上做有限加权和。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 round 172 的主问题不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值，而是寻找一个新的 `<0.25x` 结构槽位来挑战现有 low-cost anchor。相对 r171 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在相同轻 trunk + 轻 routed recipe 下，加回一个更便宜的 shared bottleneck 分支，是否比纯 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更值得”。本地成本自检显示该候选在当前 1024x4096 proxy 下 selection_accesses=527360、deployment_accesses=393216、combined_accesses=920576，对应 combined_ratio 约 `0.22x`，明确落在当前 `<0.25x` 主战场内；而历史上同 family 在更宽 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、同 `K=96/TRUNK_RANK=16` 下已给过 `FVU=0.1463` 的弱正信号，明显比 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 在同 target 上的强负信号更值得用当前更轻 recipe 复验。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 `0.22x` 下把 FVU 压到接近或优于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=80/96` anchors，则下一轮继续留在该 family，只改 `K`，定位它在 `<0.25x` 内的 deployment knee。","如果该点仍明显弱于同成本 anchors，则可更明确地下调 `shared bottleneck + routed expert` 这条 hetero-MoE 方向的优先级，后续转向别的低成本 architecture probe，而不是继续在它上面做局部参数细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["r168-r171 已连续给出同一 low-cost 邻域内的局部负信号：继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 轴补点，信息增量已经较低。","`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的导出形式仍是静态 shared 低秩库加静态 routed expert 子库上的有限加权和，应按 LUTurbo `扩展兼容` 处理。","本地成本自检：在 r171 的轻量 recipe 上切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，combined_ratio 约 `0.22x`，仍稳居 `<0.25x` 主战场；该 family 的 override/wiring 也已在历史轮次中跑通过，无需代码改动。","相较于 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 已经出现的更强低成本负信号，`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 仍保留更高的信息价值，因为它只对 shared 分支做 low-rank 化，而没有继续 factorize routed experts。"],"reference_round":171,"self_review":"这轮严格只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，满足 param_only 约束。选择 r171 而不是 r165/r152，是为了把比较聚焦在当前最相关的轻量 recipe 上，直接回答“在同样 `<0.25x` 预算下，shared bottleneck 是否比纯 lowrank+expert 更有价值”。主要风险是这条 hetero-MoE 线在当前更轻 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 下仍会重复历史弱信号；但如果不做这一步，就无法排除当前高优先级结构方向里最贴近 low-cost 主战场的一个候选。","summary":"以 r171 为 reference，仅切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变的前提下，执行一个新的 matched-cost low-cost architecture probe，测试 `shared bottleneck + expert-specific head` 是否能在约 `0.22x` 成本下优于当前同带 anchors。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:33277:research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3993:research/history/logs/agent_round_0141.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接做一次 matched-cost hetero-MoE 结构对照，回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head”这条线在约 0.30x total_cost 下是否能形成比当前 low-cost anchor 更有价值的新结构段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.30x 下明显优于现有 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 邻近锚点，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 继续压低 shared/routed 成本。","如果该点仍被当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier 支配，则可更明确地下调“无 residual 的 shared-lowrank+routed”优先级，把后续预算转回别的结构槽位，而不是继续在这条 family 上做局部扫参。","如果结果介于 r123 与当前 0.30x anchor 之间，则说明 shared low-rank basis 有一定价值但单独不足以形成新段；后续应优先考虑带 residual 的版本或新的 staged expert 结构，而不是再压同一 recipe。"],"notes_to_memory":["r139-r140 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮未形成新非支配点；本轮按策略切回新的结构假设对照，而不是继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩。","本轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做旧 family 局部微调，而是以当前低成本 reference r123 为 matched baseline，直接重验更符合当前 agenda 的 hetero MoE 结构 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。","本地成本自检：在 r123 配方下切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 后，selection_accesses=794624、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1253376，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.30，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":123,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 已连续两轮未形成新非支配点后，继续沿同一 family 做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K` 的局部扫参信息增量偏低；切回 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做 matched-cost architecture swap，更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和对 hetero MoE 的明确优先级。主要风险是该 family 先前在更高容量配方下已有负信号；但当前这次是更低成本、与 low-cost anchor 严格对照的重验，结论会更清晰。","summary":"建议以 r123 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。这是一轮面向低成本前沿的 matched-cost 结构对照，用当前最相关的 low-cost anchor 直接回答“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否值得继续，而不是继续在最近连续失利的 residual 变体上做局部压缩。","touched_files":[]}
