research/history/round_summaries/round_0189.json:35:      "`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式是静态 shared low-rank trunk library 与静态 routed expert 子库上的有限加权和，应继续按 `扩展兼容` 处理。",
