research/history/round_summaries/round_0138.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{l∈S_res(r1(x))} γ_l(x) c_l，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，r1(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i-Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}；U={u_i} 是静态 shared low-rank library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_l} 是静态 residual library。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量 routed experts 选择 + 静态库查表加权和 + 选择性 residual 补偿”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前最有信息量但尚无最小原型的槽位，不是再扫现有 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 hidden/K 邻域，而是给这条 hetero MoE 线补上一段全局 residual cleanup。相对 r134 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.60x total_cost 的中低成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0138.json:20:    "summary": "已在 `sparsify/` 落盘最小新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`：把当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 接上一段全局 sparse residual cleanup。建议本轮以 r134 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，先做一次干净的 matched architecture swap，直接判断“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual”是否值得继续。",
